fn.p:
Nine initial themes were drawn out based on groupings facilitated by the NVivo process:


Power of the audience to influence play – musicians’ comments;

Power of the audience to influence play – audience comments;

The impact of the venue on the gig – audience comments;

The impact of the venue on the gig – musicians’ comments;

What the musicians think the audience think about them and want from jazz gigs;

What the audience thinks jazz musicians think and want from them and what the audience actually say they want from jazz gigs;

The nature of jazz – comments from audience on their feelings about the genre and why they attend live jazz performance;

Experiences in the moment of play – musicians’ comments;

Experiences in the moment of play – audience comments.
